textBeforeTable: Optional Files (7) CUSTOM_CLASS_COLORS support - added - added class color support for suffix texts - fixed bug where modules were white when logging in with them locked 1.0 beta 2 - ack! accidentally had a generic variable as a global. that could have cause some problems... 1.0 beta 3 - updated libs and TOC number 1.0 beta 4 - added font shadow option - updated SharedMedia widgets for options - nice new looks! - per-module options are in! not for colors though 1.1 - bumped TOC number - updated libs 1.1.1 - updated libs 1.1.2 - there is a new tooltip for the latency module, showing both UI and World latency (you can disable it in options) - latency module now uses World Latency in its display 1.2 - updated TOC number - updated libs 1.2.1 - changed "THICK OUTLINE" to "MONOCHROME OUTLINE" - removed "MONOCHROME" font flag because it crashes the client currently - updated libs - updated TOC number for
